<%= form_with url: "#{@current_studio.path}/random" do |form| %>
  <p>
    Randomness is often the fairest (and funnest) way to make a decision.
    <br/>
    Select <strong>coin toss</strong> for binary decisions,
    <strong>names from a hat</strong> for selection from a list,
